      "id": "DS0009",
      "name": "Process",
      "component": "OS API Execution",
      "detects": "Monitor for API calls associated with detecting token manipulation only through careful analysis of user activity, examination of running processes, and correlation with other endpoint and network behavior, such as LogonUser and SetThreadToken. Correlate activity with other suspicious behavior to reduce false positives that may be due to normal benign use by users and administrators.",
      "url": "/datasources/DS0009"
